<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Come join your team on TeamRockett!</h1>
    <p>
       <%= @invitation.name %>,
      You have been invited to join your team:<BR>
      <h1>@invitation.organization.name</h1>
      on TeamRockett.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      Since you are new to TeamRockett, please register here <%= @reg_url %> and you will be added to your team.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you already use TeamRockett but with a different email address, please click here to sign in and request your existing account be added to your team: <%= @sign_in_url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>